Name: DobbyxEscape: Pirate Adventure
About the game: DobbyxEscape: Pirate Adventure Ahoy, Me Hearties! Tommy wants to be a pirate when he grows up! With the help of a Blue Moon, the tap of his magic wand and his great great great grandfather's pirate hat, his dreams come true! Follow Tommy on the adventure of a lifetime where he meets the legendary pirate Blackbeard! All Hands Ahoy! Features: Room Escape game! Six locations to discover! Beautiful graphics bring the game to life! Many items to collect and puzzles to solve! Fun soundtrack and sound effects!
